OL,3,CPrisons overcrowding crisis: Why are
OL,4,Csome criminals being released early?
OL,6,FThe Government is set to free around
OL,7,F1,700 prisoners on Tuesday from jails
OL,8,Facross England and Wales in a bid to
OL,9,Fcut overcrowding.
OL,11,FThis is in addition to around 1,000
OL,12,Fprisoners who are typically freed each
OL,13,Fweek.
OL,15,F` What is happening and why?
