OL,3,CPrisons overcrowding crisis: Why are
OL,4,Csome criminals being released early?
OL,6,FJustice Secretary Shabana Mahmood
OL,7,Fannounced plans in July to temporarily
OL,8,Fcut the proportion of sentences
OL,9,Finmates must serve behind bars from
OL,10,F50% to 40% as the Ministry of Justice
OL,11,F(MoJ) said overcrowding had pushed
OL,12,Fjails to the "point of collapse".
OL,14,FOn Monday, Downing Street said the
OL,15,Fpolicy had to be brought in to avoid
OL,16,F"unchecked criminality" where the
OL,17,Fpolice and courts are unable to lock
OL,18,Fanyone up.
OL,20,F` When will prisoners be released and
OL,21,Fhow many?
