OL,3,CPrisons overcrowding crisis: Why are
OL,4,Csome criminals being released early?
OL,6,FAround 1,700 will be freed on Tuesday,
OL,7,Fwith a similar number also anticipated
OL,8,Fto be freed in October.
OL,10,F` What types of criminals could be
OL,11,Ffreed?
OL,13,FThe Government said the policy will
OL,14,Fnot apply to those convicted of sex
OL,15,Foffences, terrorism, domestic abuse or
OL,16,Fsome violent offences.
