OL,6,FThis is despite Prime Minister Sir
OL,7,FKeir Starmer repeatedly insisting
OL,8,Fperpetrators of the violence would
OL,9,Ffeel the "full force of the law".
OL,11,FWhile there is no specific exclusion
OL,12,Ffor rioters, those convicted of
OL,13,Fserious violence and serve sentences
OL,14,Fof four years and over, or a terrorism
OL,15,Foffence, will be excluded, officials
OL,16,Fsaid.
