OL,3,CPrisons overcrowding crisis: Why are
OL,4,Csome criminals being released early?
OL,6,FIf prisoners breach their licence
OL,7,Fconditions ` a set of rules which they
OL,8,Fmust adhere too once out of jail
OL,9,Ftypically including restrictions on
OL,10,Ftheir movements and who they speak to
OL,11,F` they could find themselves back
OL,12,Fbehind bars. This is called being
OL,13,Frecalled to custody.
OL,15,FDepending on the breach, if they have
OL,16,Fcommitted another crime, they could be
OL,17,Finvestigated by the police and
OL,18,Fprosecuted so could end up back in
OL,19,Fcourt, facing more time behind bars.
