OL,3,CPrisons overcrowding crisis: Why are
OL,4,Csome criminals being released early?
OL,6,FAnyone recalled to prison has to be
OL,7,Fconsidered for release by the Parole
OL,8,FBoard before they can be freed again.
OL,10,F` Will this solve the problems with
OL,11,Fovercrowding?
OL,13,FNo, it will only ease capacity
OL,14,Fproblems in the short term.
OL,16,FPrison figures have warned the move
OL,17,Fwill only buy time for about a year
OL,18,Fbefore the same issue could be faced
OL,19,Fagain so there are calls for longer
OL,20,Fterm strategies to address the number
OL,21,Fof people being held behind bars.
